Package: pybackpack
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, rdiff-backup (>= 0.12.7), python-gtk2, python-glade2, python-gnome2, python-brasero, genisoimage
Description: user friendly file backup tool for GNOME
 A graphical tool to make file backup simpler. Provides a
 user-friendly interface to rdiff-backup which allows you
 to back up your files easily to an archive, to a CD/DVD
 or to a remote location using SSH.
